{"tid":919623,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[陳雲係痴線架] 兩年前陳雲講DQ販民講焦土講取消美港關係法 呢度的痴線佬都話陳雲係痴線佬","createTime":"2018-11-28T07:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T08:44:15.000Z","uid":57723,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ca26fee1012344e82d676e9a9878309c7946247a","tid":919623,"uid":57723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:41:03.000Z","msg":"今日各位講緊乜野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac200c5e375e1a3251ea6f4c2a196efc7a4402a","tid":919623,"uid":62537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:52:18.000Z","msg":"焦土唔投泛民個個都講架啦，關佢撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2089987e5eb4f92d04b49365bf57c699cf0c50","tid":919623,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:04:33.000Z","msg":"又喺度認屎認屁，得云伯一個講？<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%EF%BC%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25EF%25BC%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25AD%2596%25E6%25B3%2595&d=FCE3QmlYR159ByaDNFjom6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6bd9c2e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%EF%BC%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E6%B3%95</a><br />\n<br />\n早在2004年，全國人大常委會否決0708雙普選後，美國國會曾討論重訂香港關係法，主要由共和黨議員薩姆&middot;布朗巴克推動[2]。<br />\n<br />\n2013年斯諾登事件後，陶傑認為美國可能廢除香港關係法以反擊[13]。2015年，美國國會及行政當局中國委員會指，北京政府「8.31決定」介入香港政制發展，並指控香港警察在雨傘運動期間攻擊示威者，建議美國重新考慮香港獨立地位之條款[14]。2016年，同一委員會指，因應香港議員被取消資格及銅鑼灣書店事件，或須修改香港關係法[15]。中華人民共和國外交部強烈不滿和堅決反對上述報告，表示中國政府堅定不移貫徹一國兩制方針，香港事務屬於中國內政，任何外國無權干涉[16][17]"},{"pid":"b8bcf3dc317e31f3c300162c0b8b7bc4363554ce","tid":919623,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:06:16.000Z","msg":"傻根只係一個憤怒的葡萄,同下佢d youtube片幾多view就知佢影響力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c83723d2598479c0a3a5fada8c3c822d95a469a","tid":919623,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:44:15.000Z","msg":"Grandiose delusion唔一定句句都錯，請多加了解精神病"}]}